{"tid":868294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（女人揸車）驚！女駕車打錯檔衝進全國電子　門市滿目瘡痍","createTime":"2018-10-19T10:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T11:56:16.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"18dba4965e5befa9eea1ac72bc4afa948673d709","tid":868294,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T10:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/19/184815_39f76e55c89fc477b3d619b698a62bf5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F19%2F184815_39f76e55c89fc477b3d619b698a62bf5.png&h=7df6adc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n桃園市中壢區成章一街的全國電子門市，昨（17）日下午4時許，突然有一輛自小客飛衝至店內，店面玻璃碎裂一地，並撞毀不少家電用品，店內的客人與店員都嚇了一大跳，所幸無人員受傷。<br />\n <br />\n警方初步了解，陳姓女駕駛當時把車子停在全國電子門市的大門前，購物結束出來後上車，準備發動車子要倒退時，卻不慎打錯檔位，打到前進的D檔，一踩油門後車子就直接往店裡衝去，等到她踩煞車停下時，已撞破玻璃大門。<br />\n <br />\n陳女配合警方酒測，酒測值為零，陳女表示，因打錯檔不慎衝到店內很不好意思，造成店家損失的部份會負責賠償。"},{"pid":"047d06b688369aa81f53b82676169690a93eec75","tid":868294,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:51:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/758Y3qGecX4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F758Y3qGecX4&d=JNKOYaxhaqxPleht%2BagRY8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=2de2416f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/758Y3qGecX4</a>"},{"pid":"226f6dc771d394b36cdb8004d8465cfe20c1e07a","tid":868294,"uid":810,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:54:41.000Z","msg":"女人比錯油=<br />\n<br />\n啊！！！！！啊！！！！！(keep住比油)"},{"pid":"e17145273c73ecc59e6a0506d5527513e25df4af","tid":868294,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787cc2e2d8214591728e84d3e303c568600f6bad","tid":868294,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:56:16.000Z","msg":"豐田都咁好鋼水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}